metadata.name: LOVE, KNIVES, MISSILES
metadata.description:
expressing my pain and frustration over the things that happened not so long ago. I was spontaneously dumped by the woman I loved, betrayed by the friends I trusted, my home country was invaded on a full-scale, the war began. lots of tears here

kids, please  
fall in love only if you love yourself  
choose your friends wisely  
don't start wars

be yourself  
love

digital / 3000x3000px  
szkandal / 2023
